{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_04_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 まだ帰りたくない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もう夜か、そろそろ帰る準備をしないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's night already‚ we need to get ready to leave……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.7477551142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は凄く楽しかったよ\n海でこんなに遊んだのは初めてだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had a great time today.\nI've never played so much in the ocean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5477551142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 11.5144217808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、提案した甲斐があったよ\nそれにしても葵がこんなにはしゃぐのはめずらしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was worth suggesting.\nStill‚ it's rare to see Aoi so excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "僕だってフラストレーションが溜まって\n思い切り羽目を外したくなることもあるさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have my moments of frustration\nwhen I want to get off on the wrong foot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 25.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "この間も言ったけど\n星見プロの中で僕と莉央は業界歴が長い方だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I said the other day‚\nme and Rio have been in the industry for a long time‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "これでも先輩として\n後輩に遠慮して気を遣ってるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a senior‚\nI'm still reserved and considerate of my juniors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遠慮？　葵が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Reserved?　Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "その反応は不愉快だね。僕だって愛やこころの前では\nいい先輩でありたいと思ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I find that reaction distasteful. I too want to\nbe a good senior in front of Ai and Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって気を遣って溜め込んだものを\n時々思い切り発散したくなるのさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes I just need to vent all the stuff I've built up\nfrom taking care of myself like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 55.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それで海で遊びたいなんて言い出したのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you said you wanted to play in the ocean. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でもリズノワの四人で沖縄に行ったんだろ？\nみんなと海で遊んで満足しなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you went to Okinawa with the four of us from LizNoir‚ didn't you?\nNot satisfied with playing in the ocean with everyone else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、沖縄でみんなと遊べたのは楽しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it was fun to hang out with everyone in Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "でもみんなと遊ぶのと、君と二人で遊ぶのだと\n違う楽しさがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there's a different kind of fun when I play with everyone else\nand when I play with you alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "僕が遠慮せずにふざけたり、からかったり\n甘えられる相手は君だけなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You are the only person I can joke around with‚\ntease‚ and spoil without hesitation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "……だから、今日は君と遊べて本当に楽しかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… so it was really fun playing with you today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "気の置けない相手と海で遊ぶのが\nこんなに楽しいとは思わなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought it would be so much fun to play in the ocean with someone\nyou feel so comfortable with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\n少しは葵の役に立てたのなら良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right ……\nI'm glad I could help Aoi a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "遊ぶのは日が暮れるまでの約束だったね\nもっと君と遊んでいたかったけど……残念だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You promised to play until sunset.\nWish I could have played with you more‚ but …… too bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ、そろそろ帰ろうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… Well‚ it's time to go home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……って、その格好で帰るつもりか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ ……‚but you're going home looking like that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、楽し過ぎて着替えるのを\nすっかり忘れてたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh right‚ I was having so much fun\nI completely forgot to change my clothes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "今から着替えるのも面倒だから\nこのまま電車に乗って帰っても――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too much trouble to change my clothes now‚\nso I can just get on the train and go home――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ダメに決まってるだろ。ちゃんと着替えなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not. Get dressed properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ\nまったく、君は細かいことを気にし過ぎなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All right‚ all right.\nYou're too concerned with the details.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ僕は着替えて来るから、君は適当に時間潰してて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll go get changed‚ you just kill some time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.666666700002,
          "startTime": 142.8
        }
      ]
    },
