      "text": "それなんだけど……\nせっかくだから、帰る前に夕食を食べて行かないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's it. ……\nSince we're here‚ why don't we have dinner before we leave?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
