      "text": "戻る途中にレストランがあるから\nレポーターの仕事を頑張ったご褒美に俺がおごるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a restaurant on the way back‚\nand as a reward for all your hard work as a reporter‚ I'll treat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
