      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "今日は遊び過ぎて仕事する元気は残ってないよ\nだから、もう少しここでのんびりしていくつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've had too much fun today to have any energy left to work.\nSo‚ I'm going to relax here a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
